Introduction: - To select a new consultancy firm to consult on e-governance projects in the School Education and Sports Department. A meeting of the Project Implementation Committee was held on 5.8.2022. According to the decision taken in the meeting, the consulting company Emst & Young was selected. The company has also been given extensions from time to time.
Accordingly, the payment of service charge to the company's technical suppliers was under the consideration of the government. Accordingly, SAAT is being done as follows.
